'''沙利纳·皮康'''（{{lang-fr|Charline Picon}}，{{bd|1984年|12月23日||}}）是一名[[法国|法国]]女子RS:X级[[帆板|帆板]]运动员<ref name=london2012>{{cite web|title=Charline Picon|url=http://www.london2012.com/athlete/picon-charline-1079606/|work=[[London_2012|London 2012]]|accessdate=8 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407021714/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/picon-charline-1079606/|archivedate=2013年4月7日}}</ref><ref>{{cite sports-reference | 1 = Charline Picon | 2 = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/pi/charline-picon-1.html | 3 = 8 September 2013 | url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/pi/charline-picon-1.html | accessdate = 2016-08-16 | archive-date = 2013-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922110927/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/pi/charline-picon-1.html }}</ref>，赢得[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會帆船女子風浪板比賽|2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會帆船女子風浪板比賽]][[金牌|金牌]]及2020年夏季奧林匹克運動會帆船女子風浪板比賽[[銀牌|銀牌]]，她也获得过[[世界帆板锦标赛|世界帆板锦标赛]]一枚金牌、两枚銀牌和三枚銅牌。<ref>{{cite news|title=Nick Dempsey and Marina Alabau conquer the 2009 RS:X World Championships|url=https://www.surfertoday.com/windsurfing/nick-dempsey-and-marina-alabau-conquer-the-2009-rsx-world-championships|publisher=Surfer Today|date=11 September 2009|accessdate=8 September 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917123227/https://www.surfertoday.com/windsurfing/nick-dempsey-and-marina-alabau-conquer-the-2009-rsx-world-championships|archive-date=2013-09-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bryony misses out on podium|url=http://www.dorsetecho.co.uk/sport/afloat/afloatnews/8373265.Bryony_misses_out_on_podium/|publisher=[[Dorset_Echo|Dorset Echo]]|date=6 September 2010|accessdate=8 September 2013|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919235456/http://www.dorsetecho.co.uk/sport/afloat/afloatnews/8373265.Bryony_misses_out_on_podium/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Charline Picon titrée en RS:X|trans_title=Charline Picon takes RS:X title|language=fr|url=http://www.lequipe.fr/Voile/Actualites/Charline-picon-titree-en-rs-x/384288|publisher=[[L'Equipe|L'Equipe]]|date=7 July 2013|accessdate=8 September 2013|archive-date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823021331/http://www.lequipe.fr/Voile/Actualites/Charline-picon-titree-en-rs-x/384288|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在[[2012年伦敦奥运会|2012年伦敦奥运会]]上获得第八名。

